+/**
+ * blink_time_show() - ``blink_time`` device attribute show function.
+ * @dev:	The LED device
+ * @attr:	The ``blink_time`` attribute (@dev_attr_blink_time)
+ * @buf:	Output buffer
+ *
+ * Writes the current value of the LED's @blink_msec to @buf.
+ *
